{"tid":1001614,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"「尐」你老母","createTime":"2019-01-30T09:30:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-30T21:04:20.000Z","uid":106675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"97488c1d67a3fa56a6afd0b7aa4a0674e3f351e7","tid":1001614,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:30:46.000Z","msg":"香港近年來隨著中港矛盾升溫，以及政府落力推行普通話教中文，坊間牽起一股捍衛粵語的思潮。一些人為了證明粵語比普通話「更古雅」，於是開始埋首於歷代韻書典籍之中，考據一些粵語口語的本字。其實粵語口語本來寫法的考據工作，一直有人在做，著作亦不少，可是現時網上有些聲稱「本字」﹑「正字」，經不起學理推敲，有些甚至令人匪而所思。<br />\n<br />\n本文今次所談的字，便是網上時常見到有人用，甚至網絡媒體《熱血時報》也當「正字」用的「尐」字。不少人直接用這個「尐」字，取代坊間常用的粵語替代字「啲」字，問題是這真是「啲」字的「正寫」嘛？「尐」字的實際讀音究竟是甚麼？粵語口語中有無用這個「尐」字的案例？「啲」字的本字其實又是甚麼？這些都是本文將會探討的問題。<br />\n<a href=\"https://jonathanovsky.wordpress.com/2014/04/12/%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%90%E3%80%8D%E5%AD%97%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%82/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fjonathanovsky.wordpress.com%2F2014%2F04%2F12%2F%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%25B0%2590%25E3%2580%258D%25E5%25AD%2597%25E4%25B9%258B%25E4%25BA%2582%2F&d=CddLi1wVc%2F0RDzQLDYdfB4kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=476cfe83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://jonathanovsky.wordpress.com/2014/04/12/%E3%80%8C%E5%B0%90%E3%80%8D%E5%AD%97%E4%B9%8B%E4%BA%82/</a>"},{"pid":"8befbaeab6c70a790d913d92bcba7d77134360c1","tid":1001614,"uid":106675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T09:32:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://the-sun.on.cc/cnt/lifestyle/20120715/photo/0715-00485-001b3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthe-sun.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20120715%2Fphoto%2F0715-00485-001b3.jpg&h=93ee47d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1256319_1_L_20160424173208.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1256319_1_L_20160424173208.jpg&h=12dd41a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n兩大「尐」字閪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff65f4e02f13e4d7efe753e20c4ae210e730035","tid":1001614,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-30T21:04:20.000Z","msg":"我唔明，有啲粵語詞根本冇對應漢字，點解一定要所謂「溯本尋源」咁生安白造個古僻漢字畀佢？"}]}